Simple Minded – Terms of Service
Effective Date: 5/20/2025

By using the Simple Minded Discord bot, you agree to the following terms:

1. Usage
You must comply with Discord’s Terms of Service and Community Guidelines.

You agree not to misuse the Bot or use it for any illegal or harmful activities.

2. Data
Some commands require temporary access to user data (e.g., User ID, timestamps).

The fishing simulator permanently stores limited data to provide game functionality.

By using these commands, you consent to this data being stored as described in the Privacy Policy.

3. Availability
The Bot may be updated or taken offline at any time without notice.

Features may be added or removed without prior warning.

4. Beta Testing
Certain features may only be accessible to designated app testers. These features may be incomplete or unstable. You may not apply to be a beta tester.

5. Data Removal
You may request deletion of any stored data by emailing evilduckperson@gmail.com or direct messsaging evilduckperson on Discord with your Discord User ID and request.
